snippet.title: Starship Home - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Here's your look at Starship Home in this trailer for the upcoming VR game. The trailer showcases how you can turn your home into a starship, embark on missions like healing alien planets, and more. Starship Home is coming to Meta Quest 3.
